{"tid":1381034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日你唔係搭港鐵嘆冷氣都唔敢啊？","createTime":"2019-07-29T07:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T08:33:06.000Z","uid":263944,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a8deaee21983b8f08f735b7ee6b7e7b57d947c96","tid":1381034,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:01:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">琴日嘅手足打生打死，我哋唔係早啲起身去港鐵歎吓冷氣都唔敢阿？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n次次有遊行，港鐵都會塞爆。<br />\n卡門，撳制，都只係阻到下，但係如果地鐵塞爆晒人，你淨係企出黎，港鐵都會癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n如果你：<br />\n忍夠不負責任既政府，<br />\n心痛元朗事件被人打到出晒血，<br />\n睇唔過警察違反人權既暴力，<br />\n不能接受縱容黑社會嘅制度。<br />\n<br />\n一齊企出黎！<br />\n只要你係調景嶺線不斷咁loop，<br />\n做到係港鐵入面遊行，港鐵就會癱瘓。<br />\n唔洗一定要著黑衫，扮係普通市民搭港鐵，<br />\n就可以減低手足既群眾壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KOa3sJn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKOa3sJn.jpg&h=501e34ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8782118f0f1da156864945dab8a161f825a293df","tid":1381034,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:01:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e36f5a0bdc2f5e6093efe6737a3031fd360c8c70","tid":1381034,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8deaee21983b8f08f735b7ee6b7e7b57d947c96","tid":1381034,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:01:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">琴日嘅手足打生打死，我哋唔係早啲